description: Maybe she is Lulu Fun, or Mary Hair, or Sybil Mann, or Hilary Queen. It's hard to keep track when you change identities more often than some people change underwear. Counterfeit Girl steals other people's identities for a living - pillaging their cyber lives, stalking them to learn and mirror their mannerisms and breaking into their homes to gather any remaining personal details. Only now someone is after her, the real her. Can she stay one step ahead of her pursuers, or has her dubious lifestyle finally caught up with her?
